beer.beer_description: Gold Medal, 2014 International Beer Challenge (London). Hawthorn Golden Ale is a full flavoured and easy drinking ale made from a combination of carefully selected German Malts which give the beer its sparkling golden appearance. Generously hopped, but mild on the bitterness, the use of three different hops from the USA, UK and Australia impart a highly refreshing passionfruit and tropical fruit character. Hawthorn Golden Ale is the perfect beer for the warmer months. Best served chilled in a glass.
